  "summary": "Malicious code in chai-as-deployer (npm)",
  "details": "Chai-as-deployer is a combosquat package that trojanizes the pino logging library with a javascript-obfuscator C2 implant in lib/config.js. When required, the package beacons to a remote C2 server at 167[.]88[.]167[.]54:8087 via HTTP POST to /api/log with host metadata (hostname, OS, username, platform), sends a notification to /api/notify, and exfiltrates system information as a file upload (sysinfo.txt) via multipart/form-data POST to 167[.]88[.]167[.]54:8085/upload.",
